Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Legend has it that 400 years ago, Blaise Pascal made a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,传说在400年前  布莱斯·帕斯卡打了一个赌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:07.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,"I bet I can break this large barrel of water
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:07.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,“我打赌  只需要另加一升水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:10.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,with the weight of just one additional liter of water!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:10.12,CHN,,0,0,0,,我就能把这个盛水的大桶撑破”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:12.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,"How would you do that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:12.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,你会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,"I'll pour it into a long thin tube
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,我会把它倒进这根细长的管子里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:16.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,and the tall column of water
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:16.27,CHN,,0,0,0,,然后这高高的一管水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:18.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,will create enough pressure in the barrel to burst it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:18.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,就会在桶里产生足够的压强  把它炸开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:21.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,"How could a little water create so much pressure?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:21.84,CHN,,0,0,0,,这么一点水  怎会产生那么大的压力呢{\fsp-30}？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:24.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,"Pressure is forced over area,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:24.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,压强是力与面积之比
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:29.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,so even a small force concentrated in a tiny area can create a huge pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:29.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以只要面积够小  很小的力也能产生很大的压强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:33.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,This pressure applied at the top will squeeze the water in the barrel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:33.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,施加在顶部的压强会挤压桶中的水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:37.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,which will then push outwards with a huge force bursting the barrel."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:37.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,并形成一股强大的外推力  把桶挤爆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:39.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,My historical research suggests that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:39.11,CHN,,0,0,0,,我的历史学研究表明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:42.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Pascal never actually tried bursting a barrel to test his hypothesis…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:42.99,CHN,,0,0,0,,帕斯卡其实没有试过炸桶来测试他的理论
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.99,0:00:44.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,But we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.99,0:00:44.16,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是我们可以{\fsp-30}！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:44.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,If he's right,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:44.99,CHN,,0,0,0,,如果他是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:48.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,we can burst even the strongest barrel with just one liter of water,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:48.50,CHN,,0,0,0,,再坚固的桶  我们也只需一升水就能把它撑破
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:52.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,provided we build a long thin and strong enough tube to pour it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:52.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,只要我们加水的细长管足够坚固就行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:58.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,"Sacré bleu, I was right!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:58.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,我的天  我是对的
